Package org.somox.sourcecodedecorator

Interface SourceCodeDecoratorRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SourceCodeDecoratorRepositoryImpl
    public interface SourceCodeDecoratorRepository
extends EObject
    A representation of the model object ' Source Code Decorator Repository'.

    The following features are supported:

    • File Level Source Code Link
    • Method Level Source Code Link
    • Control Flow Level Source Code Link
    • Interface Source Code Link
    • Component Implementing Classes Link
    • Data Type Source Code Link
    • Abstract Action Class Method Link
    • Method Level Resource Demanding Internal Behavior Link
    • Seff2 Method Mappings
    • Seff Elements Source Code Links
    See Also:
    SourcecodedecoratorPackage.getSourceCodeDecoratorRepository()
    Generated class or method.
    EMF model class or method.
